🚨BREAKING🚨
The Supreme Court of Virginia has DENIED an appeal brought by Republican State Senators that sought to undo Gov. Northam’s measures to combat COVID19. I’m proud that my team and I were able to protect these reasonable, effective, and life-saving measures. https://t.co/5vlC9c2tPh
